# Name of Student: Greg Stillwell

# Name of Project: Candlite

# Project's Purpose or Goal: (What will it do for users?)

A platform game where you jump on monsters head and kils them for gold while going though a story

# List the absolute minimum features the project requires to meet this purpose or goal:

- Jumping animations with collision detection
- Gain gold off a kill 
- Jumping on their head and making them disappear
- a health system  

# What tools, frameworks, libraries, APIs, modules and/or other resources (whatever is specific to your track, and your language) will you use to create this MVP? List them all here. Be specific.

Godot engine 

